There are good cafes nearby for lunch and breakfast & I don't think breakfast is of good value in U232 (14 euros per person).	We did not have breakfast as our rate did not include it and it was quite expensive but there are a number of local cafes and coffee shops so getting breakfast and lunch was no problem.	In business area but did have a few good restaurants nearby with lots of cafes for breakfast.	The staff was helpful, and the hotel has an attractive bar area for grabbing a drink before or after dinner.